#!/bin/bash
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="${CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-madsbk}"
export USER="${USER:-madsbk}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/madsbk}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/lib}"
export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"
export TERM="${TERM:-xterm}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/bash}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR="${XDG_RUNTIME_DIR:-/run/user/2001}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-27141}"
export _="${_:-./press.py}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/2}"
export OLDPWD="${OLDPWD:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.16.30 53273 22}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.16.30 53273 130.225.212.177 22}"
export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="1"
export BH_SLURM_NNODES="8"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-005.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Heat Equation 30k'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
#SBATCH -p med-3
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = cluster

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = cpu
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/madsbk/.local/include -I/home/madsbk/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]
type = ve
include = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

" > /tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-005.sh_0.config.ini
cd ../bohrium
mpiexec -ppn 4 -np 1  /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-005.sh-0.time python benchmark/Python/heat_equation.py --size=30000*30000*10 --bohrium=True : -np 31 ~/.local/bin/bh_vem_cluster_slave 1> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-005.sh-0.out 2> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-005.sh-0.err

#!/bin/bash
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="${CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-madsbk}"
export USER="${USER:-madsbk}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/madsbk}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/lib}"
export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"
export TERM="${TERM:-xterm}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/bash}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR="${XDG_RUNTIME_DIR:-/run/user/2001}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-27141}"
export _="${_:-./press.py}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/2}"
export OLDPWD="${OLDPWD:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.16.30 53273 22}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.16.30 53273 130.225.212.177 22}"
export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="1"
export BH_SLURM_NNODES="8"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-008.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'N-body 20k'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
#SBATCH -p med-3
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = cluster

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = cpu
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/madsbk/.local/include -I/home/madsbk/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]
type = ve
include = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

" > /tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-008.sh_0.config.ini
cd ../bohrium
mpiexec -ppn 4 -np 1  /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-008.sh-0.time python benchmark/Python/nbody.py --size=20000*10 --bohrium=True : -np 31 ~/.local/bin/bh_vem_cluster_slave 1> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-008.sh-0.out 2> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-008.sh-0.err

export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"

export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="4"

#SBATCH -J 'N-body 20k'

#!/bin/bash
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="${CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"

export TERM="${TERM:-xterm}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/bash}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR="${XDG_RUNTIME_DIR:-/run/user/2001}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-27141}"
export _="${_:-./press.py}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/2}"
export OLDPWD="${OLDPWD:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.16.30 53273 22}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.16.30 53273 130.225.212.177 22}"
export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="1"
export BH_SLURM_NNODES="8"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-011.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Shallow Water 25k'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
#SBATCH -p med-3
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = cluster

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = cpu
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/madsbk/.local/include -I/home/madsbk/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]
type = ve
include = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

" > /tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-011.sh_0.config.ini

mpiexec -ppn 4 -np 1  /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-011.sh-0.time python benchmark/Python/shallow_water.py --size=25000*25000*10 --bohrium=True : -np 31 ~/.local/bin/bh_vem_cluster_slave 1> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-011.sh-0.out 2> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-011.sh-0.err

#!/bin/bash
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="${CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-madsbk}"
export USER="${USER:-madsbk}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/madsbk}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/lib}"
export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"
export TERM="${TERM:-xterm}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/bash}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR="${XDG_RUNTIME_DIR:-/run/user/2001}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-27141}"
export _="${_:-./press.py}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/2}"
export OLDPWD="${OLDPWD:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.16.30 53273 22}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.16.30 53273 130.225.212.177 22}"
export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="4"
export BH_SLURM_NNODES="8"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-012.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Shallow Water 25k'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
#SBATCH -p med-3
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = cluster

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]

children = cpu

children = cpu

[range]

children = cpu

#!/bin/bash
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="${CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-madsbk}"
export USER="${USER:-madsbk}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/madsbk}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/lib}"
export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"
export TERM="${TERM:-xterm}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/bash}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR="${XDG_RUNTIME_DIR:-/run/user/2001}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-27141}"
export _="${_:-./press.py}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/2}"
export OLDPWD="${OLDPWD:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.16.30 53273 22}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.16.30 53273 130.225.212.177 22}"
export C_INCLUDE_PATH="${C_INCLUDE_PATH:-/home/madsbk/mpich-3.1.2/install/include}"
export OMP_NUM_THREADS="4"
export BH_SLURM_NNODES="8"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-015.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Black Scholes 100m'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
#SBATCH -p med-3
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = cluster

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = cpu
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/madsbk/.local/include -I/home/madsbk/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]
type = ve
include = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

" > /tmp/bh-job-bAHptG-015.sh_0.config.ini
cd ../bohrium
mpiexec -ppn 4 -np 1  /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-015.sh-0.time python benchmark/Python/black_scholes.py --size=100000000*10 --bohrium=True : -np 31 ~/.local/bin/bh_vem_cluster_slave 1> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-015.sh-0.out 2> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-bAHptG-015.sh-0.err
